description: This table contains ICD-10 code and diagnosis description related to the first reoperation.

columns.name: REGISTRY_DATA_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the registry data record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: NSQIP_FST_REOP_ICD10
columns.description: ICD-10 code associated with the first return to the OR.

columns.name: NSQIP_FST_REOP_ICD10_DX_DESC
columns.description: ICD-10 diagnosis description associated with the first return to the OR.
